        <p>You must not use the font software in apps or equipment that you sell or profit from.</p>
        <p>If you want to use Frutiger Light in an app, you must buy your own licence. This licence does not cover it.</p>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="nhsuk-details">
      <summary class="nhsuk-details__summary">
        <span class="nhsuk-details__summary-text">
