        </span>
      </summary>
      <div class="nhsuk-details__text">
        <p>You can install the software on servers that you control or servers that a third party controls for you.</p>
        <p>You can:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>use the font to create, edit and distribute documents or other NHS materials</li>
          <li>embed the font into electronic documents (note: digital marketing communications are covered below)</li>
          <li>create internal-only back-ups</li>
        </ul>
        <p>You must make sure that materials you create:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>do not allow any part of the font software code to be taken out</li>
          <li>only have images of the font that cannot be edited (note: Word documents are covered below)</li>
        </ul>
        <p>If you use the font, font software or materials in a collaborative cloud environment, you can let users view and edit the document but not otherwise use the font.</p>
      </div>
