    <p>If you have any issues with the font covered by these licence terms, contact <a href="mailto:england.font@nhs.net">england.font@nhs.net</a>. Do not contact Monotype. You cannot make a claim against Monotype directly.</p>

    <h2>Breaches of the licence and claims by Monotype</h2>
    <p>You must let us know immediately if you breach your licence. Contact <a href="mailto:england.font@nhs.net">england.font@nhs.net</a>.</p>
    <p>You must fix any breaches you can within 60 days.</p>
    <p>NHS England or Monotype can end your licence and rights to use the font if you breach its terms.</p>
    <p>You agree to compensate NHS England for any losses, claims or liabilities that arise if you or anyone you allow to use the font:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>misuse the font</li>
      <li>use it without being unauthorised</li>
      <li>breach the licence terms</li>
      <li>act in a way that causes NHS England to breach its contract with Monotype</li>
    </ul>
    <p>If Monotype makes a claim about your, your users' or your suppliers' use of the font, you must help us and give us any reasonable information we ask for. This may include providing a list of font users and details of how you use the font.</p> 

    <h2>Trade marks and intellectual property</h2>
    <p>The font is proprietary to Monotype and protected by UK, US and other intellectual property laws.</p>
    <p>You must not use any Monotype trade marks publicly, including the words "FRUTIGER" and "MONOTYPE", unless you have separate written consent from Monotype.</p>

